Privacy Policy  
----------------

- Introduction  
Our privacy policy will help you understand what information we collect at 'K2 Groups', how 'K2 Groups' uses it, and what choices you have.
'K2 Groups' built the 'System Info - K2' app as a free app. This APP/SERVICE is provided by 'K2 Groups' at no cost and is intended for use as is.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation with this policy. The Personal Information that we collect are used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.  
The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, which is accessible in our website, unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.

- Information Collection and Use  
We do not ask for any data or personal information for our app 'System Info - K2'.  
The app does use third party services that may collect information used to identify you. This includes any data collected by flutter framework as the app is based on flutter codebase.

- Cookies  
We do not knowingly collect personal identifiable information from any user. Third party applications might access user data in order to provide respective functionality responsibility based on that service. This is further explained in Service Providers Section.

- Location Information  
Some of the services may use location information transmitted from user's mobile phones. We only use this information within the scope necessary for the designated service.  

- Device Information  
We do not store any information from your device with us. The information that our app shows is dynamic and based on your device. We have no provision to store any data from your device running our app.  

- Service Providers  
We may employ third-party companies and individuals due to the following reasons:  
    * To facilitate our Service;
    * To provide the Service on our behalf;
    * To perform Service-related services; or
    * To assist us in analyzing how our Service is used.  

We want to inform users of the flutter sdk as a service provider for various functionality provided in our app. We do not share or collect any data to any third party service in our knowledge. However any change in privacy policy of flutter app development cycle using flutter sdk does implicitly apply to our policy as well since our app is based on flutter sdk. We also comply with google playstore policies, hence all the policies from google playstore are also applicable to our app based on its functionality, category, and other listing requirements layed by google. 

- Security  
We do not knowingly collect personal identifiable information from any user. Thus there is no security risk of data. 

- Children's Privacy  
We do not knowingly collect personal identifiable information from any children.  

- Changes to This Privacy Policy  
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately, after they are posted on this page.  

